<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="abs" id="abs">abs</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Syntaxe:
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstdlib&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">int</span> <span class="kw3">abs</span> <span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="kw4">int</span> nb<span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

La fonction <code>abs()</code> renvoie la valeur absolue de <code>nb</code>. Exemple:
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">     <span class="kw4">int</span> nb_mystere <span class="sy1">=</span> <span class="nu0">10</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
     <span class="kw3">cout</span> <span class="sy1">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="st0">&quot;Devinez : &quot;</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
     <span class="kw3">cin</span> <span class="sy1">&gt;&gt;</span> x<span class="sy4">;</span>
     <span class="kw3">cout</span> <span class="sy1">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="st0">&quot;Votre essai est à &quot;</span> <span class="sy1">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="kw3">abs</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span>nb_mystere <span class="sy2">-</span> x<span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="sy1">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="st0">&quot; du nombre mystère.&quot;</span> <span class="sy1">&lt;&lt;</span> endl<span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>
Le C++ fournit aussi les implémentations suivantes :

</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstdlib&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw3">abs</span> <span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="kw4">long</span> nb<span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span> <span class="co1">// identique à labs() en C99</span>
&nbsp;
    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span>
    <span class="co1">// les implémentations ci-dessous sont</span>
    <span class="co1">// des formes équivalentes de fabs()</span>
    <span class="kw4">float</span> <span class="kw3">abs</span> <span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="kw4">float</span> nb<span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
    <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">abs</span> <span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="kw4">double</span> nb<span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
    <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">abs</span> <span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> nb<span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>
